            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Libero Patri <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usto</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>sac</abbr><ex>rum</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Apul</abbr><ex>eius</ex></expan> Marcus <expan><abbr>dec</abbr><ex>urio</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>col</abbr><ex>oniae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>quaes</abbr><ex>tor</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>porticus cum cubiculis a vii <note>sic</note> <lb n="4"/>hostium exustos pecunia <lb n="5"/>sua ob scribatum restituit <lb n="6"/>permittente ordine
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Zeilenlinien für die Beschriftung. Datierung: nach einem Angriff der Markomannen oder Jazygen 170 n. Chr., zur Zeit der Alleinherrschaft des Mark Aurel. (B): Daicoviciu - Piso; IDR III: Leseabweichungen.</p>
            </div>
